    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Reliefs found on the face of a voussoir or keystone, so-named because they resemble the shape of a clasp or badge ("agrafe" in French).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
